Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他可是这领域最权威的专业人士\NSupposed to be a top expert in his field.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-还有一块碑  -对\N- Wait, there's another tablet? - Yes.
