Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}到底有多少神之语啊\NHow many words of God are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我一年前才成为先知的\NI just became a prophet, like, a year ago.
