Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}同样的事情  也是在明尼阿波里斯\NSame thing happens, also in Minneapolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这说明什么呢\NWhat does that tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}千万别去明尼阿波里斯\NStay out of Minneapolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}同一个城市中两个人被掏心  间隔六个月\NTwo hearts ganked, same city, six months apart.
