Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么东西\NA what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是我们的活儿\NIt's a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}咱们动身去瞧瞧吧\NLook, I say we hang out the shingle again and ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们手头有事做  迪恩\NWe're on a case, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}咱们得先找到凯文和石碑\NKevin and the demon tablet need to be found,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}掏心怪物再说吧\Nso heart guy takes a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们为了找凯文\NUh, we just spent a week chasing our asses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}已经瞎转悠一周了\Ntrying to lock Kevin down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看看我们  我们.,.\NAnd look at us. We're --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们这是在哪儿\NWhere the hell are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}农贸市场\NFarmers' market.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有机食品\NOrganic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么了  我休假一年\NWhat? I had a year off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}尽情享受美好生活来着\NI took the time to enjoy the good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}将我们的职责抛在脑后\NWhile avoiding doing what we actually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩  你每次说这话真就那么爽吗\NWow, Dean, does it make you feel that much better every time you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行了  老弟  我懂\NAll right, man, look, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你这一年做做瑜伽  弹弹琴\NYou took a year off to do yoga and play the lute,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}随便你  但现在我回来了\Nwhatever, but I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行吗  我们回来了\NOkay, we're back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我们得行走江湖  斩妖除魔\Nwhich means that we walk and kill monsters at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会找到凯文的\NWe'll find Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但在此期间我们能不管这种事吗\NBut in the meantime, do we ignore stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还是说让无辜的人死去吧\NOr are innocent people supposed to die
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就买你的农产品\Nso that you can shop for produce?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这案子怪就怪在\NHere's what's odd about this thing --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}死者身上并没有砍伤或刀伤  没有切口\NThe guy wasn't chopped or cut into, no incision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但他的心脏像颗桃核一样被揪了出来\NBut his heart was ripped out of him like a peach pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}遭抢劫了吗\NWas he robbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}手机  手表和钱都还留在身上\NPhone, watch, money all still on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有任何敌人吗\NWhat about enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是来镇里开会的  在当地没有熟人\NHe was in town for a conference. No local connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们在六个月前发现一起相同案件\NYou guys had another one of these about six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是  调查毫无结果\NYeah, and we hit a brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}实在是查不下去\NWe had nothing to go on, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本来还以为有发现\NThought maybe we got lucky here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}公园摄像头拍到了一些东西\NA park surveillance camera picked up something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那胖子是最后一个见到活着的死者的人\NThat chubby guy the last person to see the vic alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}再就是凶手了\NOther than the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他叫保罗・海耶斯\NName's Paul Hayes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们叫他来问过话\NWe pulled him in for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们为什么排除了他的嫌疑\NSo what makes you think he's clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}到目前为止没法证实与他有关\NWell, so far, no reason not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是说  他承认曾见过死者一面\NI mean, he said he briefly saw the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}超过了他  仅此而已\Nhe ran out ahead, that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是说他没有跪下来\NWhat, you mean he didn't fall to his knees
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}坦白自己把那家伙掏心了\Nand confess to gutting the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是  我们对他做了详细的背景调查\NNo. I mean we did a thorough check on the guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}连张违章停车的罚单都没有\Nnot so much as a parking ticket came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们自己看看他\NI mean, look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是说  他是挺能跑  可他又不是雷神\NI mean, sure, he can run a little bit, but Thor he ain't.
