Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}包括那两个嫌犯  共八个\NIncluding our two suspects? Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-这么多  -对\N- Eight? - Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其中一个就在博尔德  对吗\NOkay, um, and one of them's in Boulder, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}坏消息是你说错了\NYou would be wrong. That's the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好消息是布里克就住在博尔德郊区\NGood news is, Brick lived just outside of Boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是他死了\NWell, Brick's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错  可是他是唯一的线索\NYeah, but he's all we got,
