Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想说\NI just want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对您儿子的事我们深表遗憾  霍姆斯女士\Nhow sorry we are for your loss, Mrs. Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}布里克・霍姆斯可是我高中的偶像\NYou know, Brick Holmes was my idol back in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}太了不起了\NAmazing career.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}18年的职业生涯\N18 pro seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}7次分区冠军  4次夺得超级碗\N7 division championships, 4 super bowls --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}每时每刻都处在巅峰\Nnever slowed down a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}布里克就是为比赛和运动而生的\NBrick lived for competition and athletic perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想他的粉丝不会想到  他也只是凡人\NI don't think it occurred to his fans that he was human,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟我们一样\Nlike the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}您知道他是个器官捐赠者吗\NDo you know your son was an organ donor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这跟联调局有什么关系吗\NDoes that make this a matter for the FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们刚说过了\NLike we explained earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们其实是为调查另一件事而来\Nwe're mostly here to dot some I's on a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}几年前曾经有一次公众倡议活动\NThere was a public-awareness thing a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不少明星运动员都签了字\NA lot of star athletes signed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}布里克当时肯定没多想\NI'm sure Brick didn't think twice about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为他从没想过自己会死\Nsince he never thought he was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不少运动员都是这种心态吧\NA lot of jocks are like that, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我禁不住要想\NYou know, I-I can't help wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那晚桥上到底发生了什么\Nwhat happened that night on that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}车流不多\NThere was light traffic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是醉驾  也没有刹车痕\Nno alcohol involved, no skid marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一流的运动员  身手敏捷\NBig-time athlete, reflexes like a cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他怎么就冲下了大桥\Nhow is it that he just drives off the side of a bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那些意想不到的事情发生的时候\NWhen things happen that aren't supposed to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}才被称为意外吧\Nthey're called accidents, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不用说  大家都熟知布里克的职业生涯\NSo, everybody knows about Brick's football career, obviously,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他的私生活却无人知晓\Nbut no one knows much about his personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他结过婚吗\NWas he ever married?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他心里只有橄榄球  为此他付出了全部\NJust to the game. He gave it everything he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这样的生活可不容易\NIt's a difficult life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}布里克死前您留意到有什么变化吗\NDid you notice any changes in Brick before he died --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他生活中出现了什么新的人或事物吗\NYou know, anyone, anything new in his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想没有\NNo, no. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也没有新的喜好\NSo, no new interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}飞蝇钓鱼  集邮  超自然什么的\NFly fishing, stamp collecting, the occult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}超自然\NThe occult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}举个例子而已\NAs a "For instance."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}全是老样子\NEverything was just as it had been.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不好意思  我恐怕得告辞了\NI'm sorry, but I'm afraid my time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}大学要以布里克的名字命名一幢新体育馆\NThe university is naming a new athletic building after Brick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不能迟到\NI can't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然了  最后一个问题\NOf course. Just one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}问题总是问不完的  对吗\NThere is always one more question in life, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}依我的经验是如此\NThat's what I find.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她不愿多说  对吗\NOh, she didn't want to say much, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-见鬼  -怎么了\N- Son of a bitch. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来了  又出事了\NThere it is. It happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别告诉我博尔德又有人被掏心了\NCome on, don't tell me someone had their heart ripped out here in Boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行  那我就不说了\NAll right, then I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在这儿干什么  兰达\NWhat are you doing here, Randa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道我喜欢待在家附近\NYou know I like to stay close to the mother ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看见门前有辆车  就从后门进来了\NI saw a car out front, so I came in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是警察\NCops?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或许世人仍然沉迷于布里克的死吧\NI suppose Brick's death continues to fascinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}丑话说在前头\NSo we're clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说话还很谨慎吗\NYou're still being very careful about what you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我老了  兰达  但不傻\NI'm old, Randa, not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只想保护布里克\NI'm just trying to protect Brick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也是\NAnd so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}布里克的心脏在这里跳动着\NBrick's heart beats inside here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}布里克给了我新生命  我能感觉到他\NBrick gave me new life. I can feel him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我才搬来博尔德\NIt's why I moved to Boulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}靠近这里\Nto be near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会像布里克一样照顾你\NAnd I'll watch out for you like Brick did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不需要你的关心\NI don't need your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们唇齿相依  而布里克需要我们\NWe need each other, and Brick needs us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你保住我们的小秘密\NYou keep our little secret safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们三个人就会相安无事\Nand the three of us will be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  莫瑞森教授  帮大忙了\NAll right, Professor Morrison, that does it.
